name: Forest - Flags of a Future Rebellion
description:
Negative Time landscape / digital folklore artefact

Speculative timelines and perspective views woven into a single landscape image that is part painting, part cartography or folk map, and part tattered flag/sigil. Reflecting folk art traditions used to pass on information & myth across space and time.

Created by hybrid generative/manual-generative method, where i insert myself into the loop of a semi-generative process of video and feedback manipulation. 

1920x1080
